definition: in the final analysis/in the end
to speak/to say/to explain/to scold/to tell off/a theory (typically the last character in a compound, as in 日心說|日心说 heliocentric theory)
to (a place)/until (a time)/up to/to go/to arrive/(verb complement denoting completion or result of an action)
background/bottom/base/end (of the month, year etc)/remnants/(math.) radix/base

sentences.english: After all, this is male chauvinism at play in.
sentences.chinese: 说到底，这也是大男人主义在作怪了。

sentences.english: Ultimately, though, trying to muscle China into revaluing the yuan would be a mistake.
sentences.chinese: 不过说到底，强迫中国使人民币升值终将是一个错误。

sentences.english: After all,once I'm dead,I don't exist.
sentences.chinese: 说到底，一旦我死了，我就不存在。

sentences.english: After all,my body's still functioning until star two.
sentences.chinese: 说到底，我的身体一直运作到了星号二。

sentences.english: A phobia, after all, is an irrational fear.
sentences.chinese: 恐惧症说到底是一种非理性的恐惧。

sentences.english: Leading officials' style of work is essentially the question of Party spirit.
sentences.chinese: 领导干部作风问题，说到底是党性问题。

sentences.english: But reduced to its essence meditation is all about the breath.
sentences.chinese: 但是说到底，冥想支与呼吸有关。
所以说到底是谁需要鸦片酒呢？

sentences.english: But what exactly is the differentiator between experts and non-experts?
sentences.chinese: 但是说到底，究竟专家和非专家之间的区别是什么？

sentences.english: Tell me the reason. How can I drill in high quality and speed?
sentences.chinese: 你说说到底咋回事，到底怎样才能优质高速？

sentences.english: The bottom line was that Dodi paid his wages.
sentences.chinese: 说到底，他的工资是由多迪付给的。

sentences.english: To say it explicitly, impermanence rules all phenomena.
Cartoon in the final analysis, is artificial life.
sentences.chinese: 卡通说到底，是人工化的生活。

sentences.english: After all, you're not meditating to get to the breath.
sentences.chinese: 说到底，你作禅定非为理解呼吸。

sentences.english: After all, I must have prayed to the Lord far more than that taxi - driver.
sentences.chinese: 说到底，我毕竟比那出租车司机向上帝祈祷的次数多。

sentences.english: So what are the benefits of embarking on such an undertaking as I have done?
sentences.chinese: 那么说到底，我来这里所从事的事业究竟有何益处呢？
